#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:90
msgid "Privacy Policy for TrustBank.Plc"
msgstr "Política de Privacidad de TrustBank.Plc"

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:91
msgid ""
"At TrustBank.Plc, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. "
"This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected "
"and recorded by TrustBank.Plc and how we use it."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:92
msgid ""
"If you have additional questions or require more information about our "
"Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:93
msgid ""
"This Privacy Policy applies only to our online activities and is valid for "
"visitors to our website in regard to the information that they shared and/or "
"collect in TrustBank.Plc. This policy is not applicable to any information "
"collected offline or via channels other than this website."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:94
msgid "Consent"
msgstr "Consentimiento"

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:95
msgid ""
"By using our website, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to "
"its terms."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:96
msgid "Information we collect"
msgstr "Información que recopilamos"

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:97
msgid ""
"The personal information that you are asked to provide, and the reasons why "
"you are asked to provide it, will be made clear to you at the point we ask "
"you to provide your personal information."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:98
msgid ""
"If you contact us directly, we may receive additional information about you "
"such as your name, email address, phone number, the contents of the message "
"and/or attachments you may send us, and any other information you may choose "
"to provide."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:99
msgid ""
"When you register for an Account, we may ask for your contact information, "
"including items such as name, company name, address, email address, and "
"telephone number."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:100
msgid "How we use your information"
msgstr "Cómo usamos su información"

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:101
msgid "We use the information we collect in various ways, including to:"
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:103
msgid "Provide, operate, and maintain our website"
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:104
msgid "Improve, personalize, and expand our website"
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:105
msgid "Understand and analyze how you use our website"
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:106
msgid "Develop new products, services, features, and functionality"
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:107
msgid ""
"Communicate with you, either directly or through one of our partners, "
"including for customer service, to provide you with updates and other "
"information relating to the website, and for marketing and promotional "
"purposes"
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:108
msgid "Send you emails"
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:109
msgid "Find and prevent fraud"
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:111
msgid "Log Files"
msgstr "Archivos de Registro"

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:112
msgid ""
"TrustBank.Plc follows a standard procedure of using log files. These files "
"log visitors when they visit websites. The information collected by log "
"files include internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, Internet "
"Service Provider (ISP), date and time stamp, referring/exit pages, and "
"possibly the number of clicks. These are not linked to any information that "
"is personally identifiable."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:113
msgid "Cookies and Web Beacons"
msgstr "Cookies y Balizas Web"

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:114
msgid ""
"Like any other website, TrustBank.Plc uses 'cookies'. These cookies are used "
"to store information including visitors' preferences, and the pages on the "
"website that the visitor accessed or visited. The information is used to "
"optimize the users' experience by customizing our web page content based on "
"visitors' browser type and/or other information."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:115
msgid "Third Party Privacy Policies"
msgstr "Políticas de Privacidad de Terceros"

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:116
msgid ""
"TrustBank.Plc's Privacy Policy does not apply to other advertisers or "
"websites. Thus, we are advising you to consult the respective Privacy "
"Policies of these third party ad servers for more detailed information."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:117
msgid "GDPR Data Protection Rights"
msgstr "Derechos de Protección de Datos GDPR"

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:118
msgid ""
"We would like to make sure you are fully aware of all of your data "
"protection rights. Every user is entitled to the following:"
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:120
msgid ""
"The right to access – You have the right to request copies of your personal "
"data."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:121
msgid ""
"The right to rectification – You have the right to request that we correct "
"any information you believe is inaccurate."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:122
msgid ""
"The right to erasure – You have the right to request that we erase your "
"personal data, under certain conditions."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:123
msgid ""
"The right to restrict processing – You have the right to request that we "
"restrict the processing of your personal data, under certain conditions."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:124
msgid ""
"The right to object to processing – You have the right to object to our "
"processing of your personal data, under certain conditions."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:125
msgid ""
"The right to data portability – You have the right to request that we "
"transfer the data that we have collected to another organization, or "
"directly to you, under certain conditions."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:127
msgid ""
"If you make a request, we have one month to respond to you. If you would "
"like to exercise any of these rights, please contact us."
msgstr ""

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:128
msgid "Children's Information"
msgstr "Información sobre Niños"

#: .\accounts\templates\accounts\privacy_policy.html:129
msgid ""
"TrustBank.Plc does not knowingly collect any Personal Identifiable "
"Information from children under the age of 13. If you think that your child "
"provided this kind of information on our website, we strongly encourage you "
"to contact us immediately."
msgstr ""

